exceptions.exn: Wrong bullet --: Current bullet -- is not finished.

original: intros l' l Hsorted Hprefix Hin. induction l. -- inversion Hprefix. reflexivity. -- inversion Hprefix. destruct l'. ++ simpl in Hin. specialize (Hin e). assert (In e (e :: l)) by (simpl; left; reflexivity). specialize (Hin H). simpl in Hin. contradiction. ++ simpl in Hin. assert (e = e0) by (apply H0). subst. assert (Ha : sorted l). { apply (prefix_sorted _ _ Hsorted (proj2 H)). } assert (Hb : Prefix l' l) by (apply (proj2 H)). specialize (IHl Ha Hb). assert (Hin' : forall e : entry, In e l -> In e l'). { intros. specialize (Hin e1). simpl in Hin. destruct Hin; [right; apply H2 | ]; auto. } specialize (IHl Hin'). rewrite IHl. reflexivity.
